results.name: Prime-factorization representation of irreducible (non-constant) Stern-polynomials B(n,x), listed in the order of increasing index n: a(n) = A260443(A186891(n+1)).
xref: All terms are included in A206284 and in A277200 (apart from initial 3).
Cf. A277316 (conjectured subsequence), from which this differs for the first time at n=10, where a(10) = 15750 , while A277316(10) = 22050.
